<!-- When creating a new activity, make a copy of this file with appropriate name -->
<worksheet xml:id="activity-01-intro-activity">  
<title>Positive and Negative Space</title>

  <!-- Optional introduction -->
  <introduction>
    <p>
      Creating value, balancing positive and negative space
    </p>
  </introduction>
<blockquote> <p>Competencies: Students develop a balance of positive and negative space with limited instruction. They must continue working, incorporate any perceived mistakes. They use visual communication vocabulary to document their choices and use the lecture information in class to decide when the project is complete. After completing the project, the students hold a written critique to gather feedback from peers. Students have the option to go back into their project with the feedback of the instructor and peers.  </p></blockquote>


